thly_limit_dollars, period_start, enabled\",\n        \"Supports daily/weekly/monthly budget periods\",\n        \"Includes reset_behavior field\"\n      ],\n      \"dependencies\": [\n        \"DB-002\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"DB-006\",\n      \"name\": \"Cost Pricing Table\",\n      \"description\": \"Maintain Claude model pricing data\",\n      \"priority\": \"P1\",\n      \"phase\": 1,\n      \"effort\": \"2h\",\n      \"passes\": false,\n      \"category\": \"database\",\n      \"files\": [\n        \"migrations/005_create_pricing.sql\"\n      ],\n      \"acceptance\": [\n        \"Table with model_name, input_cost_per_mtok, output_cost_per_mtok, effective_date\",\n        \"Supports historical pricing changes\",\n        \"Includes version field for tracking\"\n      ],\n      \"dependencies\": [\n        \"DB-001\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"DB-007\",\n      \"name\": \"Audit Logs Table\",\n      \"description\": \"Track all API calls and configuration changes\",\n      \"priority\": \"P2\",\n      \"phase\": 1,\n      \"effort\": \"2h\",\n      \"passes\": false,\n      \"category\": \"database\",\n      \"files\": [\n        \"migrations/006_create_audit_logs.sql\"\n      ],\n      \"acceptance\": [\n        \"Table with user_id, action, resource, timestamp, details\",\n        \"Logs API key generation, config changes, alerts triggered\",\n        \"Immutable/write-only design\"\n      ],\n      \"dependencies\": [\n        \"DB-002\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"TRACK-001\",\n      \"name\": \"Token Usage Tracking\",\n      \"description\": \"Collect and aggregate Claude API token usage\",\n      \"priority\": \"P0\",\n      \"phase\": 2,\n      \"effort\": \"8h\",\n      \"passes\": false,\n      \"category\": \"tracking\",\n      \"files\": [\n        \"src/services/usage-tracker.ts\",\n        \"src/lib/claude-api.ts\"\n      ],\n      \"acceptance\": [\n        \"Track input and output tokens separately\",\n        \"Support for multiple Claude models\",\n        \"Batch updates from Claude API responses\",\n        \"Per-request metadata captured (timestamp, model, user)\"\n      ],\n      \"dependencies\": [\n        \"DB-003\",\n        \"AUTH-001\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"TRACK-002\",\n      \"name\": \"Cost Calculation Engine\",\n      \"description\": \"Calculate USD cost from token counts using current pricing\",\n      \"priority\": \"P0\",\n      \"phase\": 2,\n      \"effort\": \"4h\",\n      \"passes\": false,\n      \"category\": \"tracking\",\n      \"files\": [\n        \"src/services/cost-calculator.ts\"\n      ],\n      \"acceptance\": [\n        \"Convert tokens to USD based on model pricing\",\n        \"Support for input/output token cost multipliers\",\n        \"Handle historical pricing changes\",\n        \"Accurate to 4 decimal places\"\n      ],\n      \"dependencies\": [\n        \"TRACK-001\",\n        \"DB-006\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"TRACK-003\",\n      \"name\": \"Real-Time Usage Aggregation\",\n      \"description\": \"Compute current usage totals and daily/weekly/monthly summaries\",\n      \"priority\": \"P0\",\n      \"phase\": 2,\n      \"effort\": \"4h\",\n      \"passes\": false,\n      \"category\": \"tracking\",\n      \"files\": [\n        \"src/services/aggregator.ts\"\n      ],\n      \"acceptance\": [\n        \"Calculate today's usage and cost\",\n        \"Calculate week-to-date metrics\",\n        \"Calculate month-to-date metrics\",\n        \"Cache results with 5-minute TTL\"\n      ],\n      \"dependencies\": [\n        \"TRACK-002\",\n        \"DB-003\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"TRACK-004\",\n      \"name\": \"Usage by Model Breakdown\",\n      \"description\": \"Segment usage statistics by Claude model variant\",\n      \"priority\": \"P1\",\n      \"phase\": 2,\n      \"effort\": \"2h\",\n      \"passes\": false,\n      \"category\": \"tracking\",\n      \"files\": [\n 